sequenceDiagram
    Calendly->>Your Server: POST /webhooks/calendly (with signature header)
    Your Server->>Your Server: Verify HMAC signature using CALENDLY_WEBHOOK_SIGNING_KEY
    alt Invalid Signature
        Your Server-->>Calendly: 401 Unauthorized
    else Valid Signature
        Your Server->>Your Server: Parse payload
        Your Server->>MongoDB: Find user by calendly.userId
        Your Server->>Your Server: Process event
        Your Server-->>Calendly: 200 OK (ALWAYS)
    end